學科別分類



中文摘要
本論文是以錄音歌仔戲的表演藝術與生態、社會及歷史定位以及其起源興盛而至衰退為主要論述。進而探討普遍存在於我們的社會中的錄音歌仔戲，在歌仔戲的變遷過程隱晦且無其位置。當今我們看得到它的存在如日光歌劇團、金紋燕兄妹歌劇團等，但卻看不到它的歷史與變遷軌跡。 錄音歌仔戲源自於五O年代末，雲林縣麥寮鄉「拱樂社」。在高雄日光歌劇團的發揚之下曾經蔚為風潮。錄音戲的製作動機除經濟上的考量外，更有保護演員嗓子、教學及傳承種種配套措施。以1970年代中期，錄音歌仔戲正由內台回歸原本同時存在外台形式，舞臺歌仔戲正顯現衰微沒落，作為一個分水嶺。並以高雄「日光歌劇團」與其旁支劇團如新日光歌劇團、藝人歌劇團、金紋燕兄妹歌劇團等，簡稱「日光體系」為主要研究對象。探討錄音歌仔戲的藝術、商業及戲劇價值。 曾經流行的錄音歌仔戲，在某一時空中沒落，舞臺地位被取代。但其表演活動的文化意義是不會消逝，錄音歌仔戲的興盛與沒落，所代表的不僅僅是歌仔戲史的發展脈絡，更象徵所處時代的流行趨勢及文化特色。


英文摘要
The paper mainly illustrates the performing arts, the ecology, the social and the historical position of the Recording Taiwanese Opera. It describes its origin, its prosperity and its decline. Then the paper further discusses the Recording Taiwanese Opera in general that exists in our society, its vague and insignificant position during the Recording. Today we can see its existence such as Sunlight Opera Troupe, Jin Wenyan the Sibling Opera Troupe and so on, but we can not trace its history and vicissitude path.The Recording Taiwanese Opera dates back from the end of the 50's in the so called "Gung Yue She" in Mai Liao Village in Yunlin County. Developed under the Sunlight Opera Troupe, it once was luxuriant. Besides the economical consideration, the motives to make the recording are to protect the singer’s throat, teaching, inheritance and many other factors.In the mid 70's, the recording play Recording Taiwanese Opera returned to its original internal stage while simultaneously maintained its external stage. The stage Taiwanese Opera is appearing declining sign, which is a watershed in its development. The main research subject of the Recording Taiwanese Opera are Sunlight Opera Troupe and its branch troupes such as Gaoxiong Sunlight Troupe, Entertainer Opera Troupe, and Jin Wenyan the Sibling Opera (together called “Sunlight Group”), and their artistic, commercial and theatrical value. The Once popular Recording Taiwanese Opera declined at certain time in history, its stage status is substituted for by other art forms. However, its performance cultural significance should not dissipate, the popularity and declining of the Recording Taiwanese Opera not only represents history development of the  Taiwanese Opera, it symbolizes the fashion tendency and the cultural characteristics of its own time as well.


論文目次
緒論 6 第一章	  錄音歌仔戲的起源、興盛及現況 17第一節	  錄音歌仔戲的起源 18第二節	  錄音歌仔戲的興盛 26第三節	  錄音歌仔戲的現況 30 第二章	  錄音歌仔戲的戲劇文本 33第一節	劇本的創作動機與來源 34第二節	劇目的情節結構分析 38第三節	錄音歌仔戲與電視歌仔戲的劇本比較 61 第三章	  錄音歌仔戲的製造與成品 68第一節	錄音歌仔戲的場地與器材70第二節	錄音人員與文武場 72第三節	錄音歌仔戲的製作過程 73 第四章	  錄音歌仔戲時代定位76第一節	傳統歌仔戲的再創新(1960s~1980s) 78第二節	活躍於邊陲的錄音團(1980s~ ) 80 結論 82參考書目 85


